    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おや？　あれは……怜？　さっきから熱心に\n雑誌を読んでいるが、何を読んでるんだ？",
      "startTime": 6.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "これは世界中の不思議と謎を紹介する情報誌です\n今月号は宇宙人特集なんですよ",
      "startTime": 14.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "知ってますか？　約45万年前、古代シュメール文明に\n太陽系第12惑星ニビルから宇宙人が飛来したんです",
      "startTime": 23.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "アヌンナキと呼ばれたその宇宙人の遺伝子操作によって\n人類が作られたという説があって……",
      "startTime": 32.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待ってくれ、一体どうしたんだ？\n怜はオカルトに興味があったのか？",
      "startTime": 38.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……最近、宇宙人、未来人、超能力者と\n関わることがあってそれでいろいろ調べていたんです",
      "startTime": 47.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……何と関わったって？",
      "startTime": 52.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "宇宙人、未来人、超能力者です\nこの間話した『涼宮ハルヒ』がいる高校での話です",
      "startTime": 59.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}